  "text": "• C. Relative expression levels were calculated using the qBASE framework [CITATION_1] and either Fluc mRNA for the Rluc gene, or housekeeping genes MRPL19, SDHA and YWHAZ for the endogenous H2AFY. Primer design and validation were evaluated as described elsewhere [CITATION_2] . Every qPCR run included no-template primer-pair control samples and these were consistently negative. All primer sequences are available in Supplementary Table S2 . qPCR assays were performed at the Université de Sherbrooke Functional Genomics Laboratory.",
